In the vicinity of Itox, the capital of the Kingdom of Dimento, 
 there is an underground waterway that was drawn from the Aria River. 
 
It has been expanding for many years. There are also routes that are no longer used
 
The number of adventurers has increased due to the recent turmoil. 
It has become difficult to secure a water source. Plans to regenerate the waterway ... 
However, it turns out that there is a passage under the waterway that I have never seen 
, and strangers have begun to spring up from that passage

It was the beginning of the "spirited away incident". 
 
Hidden with a yellow rope in this neighborhood

 After that, the real purpose of this place was

The offensive and defensive balance is good, and the initial HP is high, so it is easy to handle as the first profession. 
 You can handle adventures in solo play without problems. It can be equipped with many weapons and armor, and in the future it can be specialized in either offensive or defensive roles, and it is indispensable for parties. 
 On the other hand, I don't learn magic and I'm not good at preventing magic damage. 
 
 If you change jobs with fighter skills, you can expect further success.

A technical job that uses various skills such as attacking with traps, unlocking treasure chests, stealth, and demonstration. Players need their own sense to master it. 
If you can make an accurate action with quick judgment even in battle, you can play an active part in both solo play and party play. 
 On the other hand, due to equipment restrictions, it cannot be expected to be protected. 
 
 If you change jobs with thief skills, you can expect more tricky activities.

It is a high-powered attack magic that gives damage that surpasses that of fighters, and is indispensable in battles with powerful monsters that dominate 
 battles. 
The magic of sabotage also creates an advantage in party play, and
 is a way to compensate for its low defense during solo play. 
However, magic consumes MP, defense is fragile, and solo play in the early stages is 
 for advanced players who prefer a response. 
 
 If you change jobs with mage skills , you can expect more aggressive activities.

Healing and supportive abilities keep the party in good shape and help continue the adventure. 
Recovery is important during treasure hunting in the dungeon. With the height and equipment of HP next to the fighter, it can act as a temporary substitute in the defense, save various crisis situations that come to the party, and enable the battle to be rebuilt. 
 However, the attack power is poor, and solo play in the early stages is for advanced players. 
 
 If you change jobs with priest skills, you can expect to be active both solo and at parties.

The world "Ezershan" and the world "Alvaroa" have been integrated into the world "Estor". 
 
 Due to world integration, it may be necessary to change the soul name for souls with duplicate soul names. 
Soul change target people will be asked to change the soul name after selecting soul. 
 
For unions with duplicate union names, we have changed the name of the union with low experience points to a temporary union name. 
If the union name has been changed, the union master can change the union name only once from the union management station NPC. 
 
For talk rings with duplicate talk ring names, the name of the talk ring with a new creation date has been changed to a temporary talk ring name. 
If the Token Ring name has been changed, you can change the Token Ring name only once by using the Master Talk Ring. 
 
For details, please refer to "Rename in case of duplication" described in "Notice of World Integration" on the official website. 
 
 Due to the world integration, the following functions will be suspended from the start of regular maintenance on February 16, 2016 to the end of regular maintenance on February 23, 2016. 
 
-Use of "Casino" function in adult social gathering (chip purchase, game, chip exchange) 
-Some event functions available from NPC "Million" 
-Available from NPC "Settuno" Serial code input function
